		ref: 'Isaiah 40:31',
		slug: 'isaiah',
		ch: 40,
		text: 'But they who wait for their Father shall renew their strength; they shall mount up with wings like eagles; they shall run and not be weary; they shall walk and not faint.',
		note: 'For the worship leader running on fumes: strength is renewed by waiting on the Father, not by trying harder.',
	},
	{
		ref: 'Colossians 3:23',
		slug: 'colossians',
		ch: 3,
		text: 'Whatever you do, work heartily, as for your Father and not for men, knowing that from your Father you will receive the inheritance as your reward. You are serving the Lord.',
