	{
		ref: 'Romans 12:1',
		slug: 'romans',
		ch: 12,
		text: 'I appeal to you therefore, by the mercies of our Father, to present your bodies as a living sacrifice, holy and acceptable to him, which is your spiritual worship.',
		note: 'Worship is bigger than the song — it is your whole life offered to the Father who first showed you mercy.',
	},
	{
		ref: 'Galatians 4:7',
		slug: 'galatians',
		ch: 4,
		text: 'So you are no longer a slave, but a son, and if a son, then an heir through our Father.',
